he topic of passing through the “door” will be addressed in another chapter,but if the dog ⚪︎ reaches the door of ◇, and its resonance is sincere,then ◇ will allow it to pass—in alignment with the structure of the universe.(However, for that to happen, the dog must have, at some point,a fleeting contemplation of what it means to existsomething akin to asking, “What is a human?”
