And then, that dog ⚪︎ is reborn as a human—with a new Self ⚪︎ and a new ◇.It steps into the essence ⚪︎ unique to being human,and enters the structural pattern ◇ of humanity.
⚪︎ always steps forward through ◇ into the next dimension,becoming a new ⚪︎◇ at each stage.
