According to the latest neuroscience, the information received by one’s ego ⚪︎ is filtered through the RAS ◇ (Reticular Activating System).
This ◇ functions by sorting information according to the priorities shaped by one’s past ⚪︎-directed impulses and expressions.
In other words, the way you feel, the way you perceive things, your perspective, even the raw seeds of that perspective—all of it is housed within ◇.
Even the god you believe in resides there.
It is the act of taking the appearances perceived from the outside and resonating them inward through ◇, which serves as a mirror.
最新の脳機能科学でも言われてますが、人の我⚪︎が受け取る情報はRAS◇（網様体賦活系）によってフィルタリングされています。
